{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Manage your ever-growing settlement! Use the resources at your disposal to build  structures necessary for survival: housing, production, processing, and more. When resources grow scarce, explore your surroundings for more. Create sprawling settlements, organized central villages, or anything in between- whatever works to expand your domain.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3396920/extras/gatherHeader.png?t=1737555833\" /></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Collect resources to build new structures and keep your settlers alive. Resource management is essential for a thriving settlement.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3396920/extras/gatherGif.gif?t=1737555833\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3396920/extras/buildHeader.png?t=1737555833\" /></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Add new structures! There are 5 main types: housing, production, exploration, services, and processing. Placement is key for survival- can you maximize efficiency and still keep your settlement looking pretty?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3396920/extras/buildGif.gif?t=1737555833\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3396920/extras/exploreHeader.png?t=1737555833\" /></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Clear away the unknown to discover more resources and fresh landscapes in a limitless procedural world that grows with your settlement.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3396920/extras/exploreGif.gif?t=1737555833\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3396920/extras/recruitHeader.png?t=1737555833\" /></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Use Influence to recruit new settlers to your cause. Larger populations can produce more resources, but need more food and housing to survive!\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3396920/extras/recruitGif.gif?t=1737555833\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>Note: Settler's Domain is still early in development, and this page is likely to change often in the coming months.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3396920/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1737555833","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3396920/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1737555833","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3396920/dcfa740d484c8921e82f759a902b0415cf05aed9/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1737555833","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/stor